# convex/_generated IS committed: `convex deploy --cmd 'next build'` pushes the
# backend but does not write _generated to disk before the build runs, so the
# committed copy is what `next build` resolves `@/convex/_generated/*` against.
# `npx convex dev` / `codegen` refresh it locally; commit the change when schema
# or functions move.
